        <field name="Prerequisite"  table="yes"><text>No value</text></field>
        <field name="Location" table="yes">
          <text>Leg</text>
        </field>
        <field description="yes" name="Description">
          <text>The feet are made unusually durable. They will not develop blisters nor get tired, even when doing heavy work. Stubbing a toe or having your feet stepped on will no longer be as painful and is much less likely to cause injury.</text>
        </field>
      </datum>
